      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fenwick%2C_Connecticut"
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "text": "Surrounded by water on three sides, Fenwick evolved from a saltwater farm to a railroad‑connected enclave for Connecticut’s elite.",
